---
title: Southwest-Inspired Cheesy Beef and Bacon Burgers with Ranch-o-Mole Sauce and Monterey Jack
description: These stacked cheesy beefy burgers come with a custom made guacamole-ranch sauce! There will be plenty of sauce left over for dipping your seasoned wedges into!
